M|Gene|tx|Reference for using AI im generators, vd generators, and code-based vd tools to produce ad visuals at scale.
M|Gene|tx|---
M|When|tx|\| Need \| Tool Category \| Best Fit \|
M|When|tx|\|------\|---------------\|----------\|
M|When|tx|\| Static ad images (banners, sl) \| im generation \| Nano Banana Pro, Flux, Ideogram \|
M|When|tx|\| Ad images w/ text overlays \| im generation (text-capable) \| Ideogram, Nano Banana Pro \|
M|When|tx|\| Short vd ad (6-30 sec) \| vd generation \| Veo, Kling, Runway, Sora, Seedance \|
M|When|tx|\| vd ad w/ voiceover \| vd gen + voice \| Veo/Sora (native), or Runway + ElevenLabs \|
M|When|tx|\| Voiceover tracks for ad \| Voice generation \| ElevenLabs, OpenAI TTS, Cartesia \|
M|When|tx|\| Multi-language ad versions \| Voice generation \| ElevenLabs, PlayHT \|
M|When|tx|\| br voice cloning \| Voice generation \| ElevenLabs, Resemble AI \|
M|When|tx|\| pd mockups and variations \| im generation + references \| Flux (multi-im reference) \|
M|When|tx|\| Templated vd ad at scale \| Code-based vd \| Remotion \|
M|When|tx|\| Personalized vd (name, data) \| Code-based vd \| Remotion \|
M|When|tx|\| br-consistent variations \| im gen + style refs \| Flux, Ideogram, Nano Banana Pro \|
