M|Nano|tx|Google DeepMind's im generation md, available through the Gemini ap.
M|Nano|**Be|** hi-qual ad images, pd visuals, text rendering
M|Nano|ap|** Gemini ap (Google AI Studio, Vertex AI)
M|Nano|**Pr|** ~$0.04/im (Gemini 2.5 Flash im), ~$0.24/4K im (Nano Banana Pro)
M|Nano|**St|**
M|Nano|it|Strong text rendering in images (logos, headlines)
M|Nano|it|Native im editing (modify existing images w/ pm)
M|Nano|it|Available through the same Gemini ap used for text generation
M|Nano|it|Supports both generation and editing in one md
M|Nano|**Ad|**
M|Nano|it|gn sl media ad images from text descriptions
M|Nano|it|cr pd mockup variations
M|Nano|it|Edit existing ad images (swap backgrounds, change colors)
M|Nano|it|gn images w/ hl text baked in
M|Nano|**AP|**
M|Nano|tx|```bash
M|Usin|curl|//generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/md/gemini-2.5-flash-im:generateContent" \
M|Usin|-H "|application/json" \
M|Usin|-H "|$GEMINI_API_KEY" \
M|Usin|tx|-d '{
M|Usin|"con|[{"parts": [{"text": "cr a clean, modern sl media ad im for a project management tool. Show a laptop w/ a kanban board if. Bright, professional, 16:9 ratio."}]}],
M|Usin|"gen|{"responseModalities": ["TEXT", "im"]}
M|Usin|tx|}'
M|Usin|tx|```
M|Usin|doc|** [Gemini im Generation](https://ai.google.dv/gemini-ap/doc/im-generation)
M|Usin|tx|---
