M|Flux|tx|\| Flux 2 dv \| ~2.5 sec \| Good \| $0.012/MP \| Rapid prototyping \|
M|Flux|tx|\| Flux 2 Klein \| Fastest \| Good \| Lowest \| hi-volume batch generation \|
