M|Voic|tx|For layering realistic voiceovers onto vd ad, adding narration to pd demos, or generating audio for Remotion-rendered videos. These tools turn ad scripts into natural-sounding voice tracks.
M|When|Many|
M|When|it|**Voiceover on silent vd** — Runway Gen-4 and Remotion produce silent output
M|When|it|**br voice consistency** — Clone a specific voice for all ad
M|When|it|**Multi-language versions** — Same ad script in 20+ languages
M|When|it|**Script iteration** — Re-record voiceover w/o reshooting vd
M|When|it|**Precise control** — Exact timing, emotion, and pacing
M|When|tx|---
M|Elev|tx|The mk leader in realistic voice generation and voice cloning.
M|Elev|**Be|** Most natural-sounding voiceovers, br voice cloning, multilingual
M|Elev|ap|** REST ap w/ streaming support
M|Elev|**Pr|** ~$0.12-0.30 per 1,000 characters depending on plan; starts at $5/month
M|Elev|**Ca|**
M|Elev|it|29+ languages w/ natural accent and intonation
M|Elev|it|Voice cloning from short audio clips (instant) or longer recordings (professional)
M|Elev|it|Emotion and style control
M|Elev|it|Streaming for real-time generation
M|Elev|it|Voice library w/ hundreds of pre-built voices
M|Elev|**Ad|**
M|Elev|it|gn voiceover tracks for vd ad
M|Elev|it|Clone your br spokesperson's voice for all ad variations
M|Elev|it|Produce the same ad in 10+ languages from one script
M|Elev|it|A/B tst different voice styles (authoritative vs. friendly vs. ur)
M|Elev|**AP|**
M|Elev|tx|```bash
M|Elev|curl|//ap.elevenlabs.io/v1/text-to-speech/{voice_id}" \
M|Elev|-H "|$ELEVENLABS_API_KEY" \
M|Elev|-H "|application/json" \
M|Elev|tx|-d '{
M|Elev|"tex|"Stop wasting hours on manual reporting. Try DataFlow free for 14 days.",
M|Elev|"mod|"eleven_multilingual_v2",
M|Elev|"voi|{"stability": 0.5, "similarity_boost": 0.75}
M|Elev|tx|}' --output voiceover.mp3
M|Elev|tx|```
M|Elev|doc|** [ElevenLabs ap](https://elevenlabs.io/doc/ap-reference/text-to-speech)
M|Elev|tx|---
