M|Code|tx|For templated, data-driven vd ad at scale, Remotion is the best option. Unlike AI vd generators that produce unique vd from pm, Remotion uses rc code to render deterministic, br-perfect vd from templates and data.
M|Code|**Be|** Templated ad variations, personalized vd, br-consistent production
M|Code|**St|** rc + ts
M|Code|**Pr|** Free for individuals/small teams; commercial license required for 4+ employees
M|Code|doc|** [remotion.dv](https://www.remotion.dv/)
M|Why |tx|\| AI vd Generators \| Remotion \|
M|Why |tx|\|---------------------\|----------\|
M|Why |tx|\| Unique output each time \| Deterministic, px-perfect \|
M|Why |tx|\| pm-based, less control \| Full code control over every frame \|
M|Why |tx|\| Hard to match br exactly \| Exact br colors, fonts, spacing \|
M|Why |tx|\| One-at-a-time generation \| Batch render hundreds from data \|
M|Why |tx|\| No dynamic data insertion \| Personalize w/ names, prices, stats \|
M|Ad C|tx|**1. Dynamic pd ad**
M|Ad C|Feed|
M|Ad C|tx|```tsx
M|Ad C|tx|// Simplified Remotion cp for pd ad
M|Ad C|expo|rc.FC<{
M|Ad C|prod|string;
M|Ad C|pric|string;
M|Ad C|imag|string;
M|Ad C|tagl|string;
M|Ad C|tx|}> = ({productName, price, imageUrl, tagline}) => {
M|Ad C|tx|return (
M|Ad C|<Abs|'#fff'}}>
M|Ad C|<Img|400, height: 400}} />
M|Ad C|tx|<h1>{productName}</h1>
M|Ad C|tx|<p>{tagline}</p>
M|Ad C|tx|<div className="price">{price}</div>
M|Ad C|tx|<div className="cta">Shop Now</div>
M|Ad C|tx|</AbsoluteFill>
M|Ad C|tx|);
M|Ad C|tx|};
M|Ad C|tx|```
M|Ad C|tx|**2. A/B tst vd variations**
M|Ad C|Rend|
M|Ad C|tx|```tsx
M|Ad C|tx|const variations = [
M|Ad C|hl|"Save 50% Today", cta: "Get the Deal", theme: "ur"},
M|Ad C|hl|"Join 10K+ Teams", cta: "Start Free", theme: "sl-proof"},
M|Ad C|hl|"Built for Speed", cta: "Try It Now", theme: "benefit"},
M|Ad C|tx|];
M|Ad C|tx|// Render all variations programmatically
M|Ad C|tx|```
M|Ad C|tx|**3. Personalized outreach videos**
M|Ad C|tx|gn videos addressing prospects by name for cold outreach or sales.
M|Ad C|tx|**4. sl ad batch production**
M|Ad C|Rend|
M|Ad C|- 1|1 for feed
M|Ad C|- 9|16 for Stories/Reels
M|Ad C|- 16|9 for YouTube
M|Remo|tx|```
M|Remo|tx|1. ds template in rc (or use AI to gn the cp)
M|Remo|tx|2. Define data sc (pd, headlines, CTAs, images)
M|Remo|tx|3. Feed data array into template
M|Remo|tx|4. Batch render all variations
M|Remo|tx|5. Upload to ad platform
M|Remo|tx|```
