M|Reco|tx|3. **Batch produce variations** w/ Remotion using data (pd, headlines, CTAs)
M|Reco|tx|4. **Iterate** — use AI tools for new angles, Remotion for scale
M|Reco|tx|This hybrid approach gives you the creative exploration of AI generators and the consistency and scale of code-based rendering.
